<doc>
  <member name="WBEM_REFRESHER_FLAGS">
    <summary>
      <para>Contains flags that modify the behavior of refresher methods.</para>
    </summary>
    <seealso cref="IWbemConfigureRefresher.Remove" />
    <seealso cref="IWbemRefresher.Refresh" />
  </member>
  <member name="WBEM_REFRESHER_FLAGS.WBEM_FLAG_REFRESH_AUTO_RECONNECT">
    <summary>
      <para>If the connection is broken, the refresher attempts to reconnect to the provider automatically.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="WBEM_REFRESHER_FLAGS.WBEM_FLAG_REFRESH_NO_AUTO_RECONNECT">
    <summary>
      <para>If the connection is broken, the refresher does not attempt to reconnect to the provider automatically.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
</doc>